<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA46">
<l>eḷiya tituvaṉṟē yēḻaikāḷ yātu</l>
<l>maḷiyī raṟivilī rāvā - voḷikoḷmiṭaṟ</l>
<l>ṟentaiyarāp pūṇṭuḻalu memmāṉai yuḷniṉainta</l>
<l>cintaiyarāy vāḻun tiṟam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This is easy, isn’t it, you fools, who do not care for,</l>
<l>who do not know anything, ohoh, the way to live as people</l>
<l>with minds that think inside of our father with the bright throat,</l>
<l>of our lord who moves about wearing a snake.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
